{"sn17.21:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 17.21 ","sn17.21:0.2":"3. Tatiyavagga ","sn17.21:0.3":"Matugamasutta ","sn17.21:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn17.21:1.2":"“Daruno, bhikkhave, labhasakkarasiloko …pe… ","sn17.21:1.3":"na tassa, bhikkhave, matugamo eko ekassa cittam pariyadaya titthati yassa labhasakkarasiloko cittam pariyadaya titthati. ","sn17.21:1.4":"Evam daruno kho, bhikkhave, labhasakkarasiloko …pe… ","sn17.21:1.5":"evanhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ","sn17.21:1.6":"Pathamam. "}